snippet.title: FIRST LOOK at SCENES of "THREE  DAYS TO KILL"- Kevin Costner, Amber Heard,Hailee Steinfeld
snippet.description:
Three Days to Kill (2013) - Action | Drama | Thriller  -  2013 (France)
A dying Secret Service Agent Ethan Runner ( Kevin Costner )  trying to reconnect with his estranged daughter is offered an experimental drug that could save his life in exchange for one last assignment.
